name: Upcycled Cork Keychain
description:
They make the perfect accessory for any set of keys. 

They are very unique gift ideas as party favors for bridesmaids gifts or anyone at a wedding and for who enjoy wine, wine collecting or wine tasting.

They are made from real recycled wine corks.

Corks are collected from around the world so they are all unique and different from each other.

Because of the nature of cork and the various methods both synthetic and real corks, every wine cork key chain is truly one of a kind, different and special

If you are interested in purchasing more than one please message me, I am willing to work with you on pricing. 

The key rings pictured are just an example you will be shipped comparable items depending on availability of styles.
